
MNIST-Dataset-Analysis/
│
├── src/
│   ├── load_data.py                 # Step 1: Load the dataset
│   ├── display_samples.py           # Step 2: Display sample images
│   ├── preprocess_data.py           # Step 3: Reshape and normalize the data
